OL,6,FA "complex, troubled and devious"
OL,7,Fwoman stabbed her husband in the back
OL,8,Ffollowing an argument at their north
OL,9,FDevon home, a court has heard.
OL,11,FChristine Rawle is on trial for the
OL,12,Fmurder of her husband, Ian Rawle, in
OL,13,FAugust 2022 near Braunton.
OL,15,FOpening the case for the jury at
OL,16,FExeter Crown Court, Sean Brunton KC
OL,17,Fopened his case by referencing the
OL,18,Fpopular Roald Dahl book 'The Twits'.
