OL,3,C'Devious' woman stabbed husband in the
OL,4,Cback after row, court told
OL,6,FHe said: "It's about a married couple
OL,7,Fwho delight in making each other's
OL,8,Flives as miserable as possible. They
OL,9,Fplay tricks on each other, they are
OL,10,Fmean to each other. But they also need
OL,11,Feach other.
OL,13,F"While The Twits is a humorous story
OL,14,Fof fiction, and this case is very
OL,15,Freal, we say the book serves to
OL,16,Fillustrate a point.
OL,18,F"That some marriages, particularly
OL,19,Fthose that have endured for many
OL,20,Fyears, are complex, not always happy
OL,21,Fand often have hidden depths.
