OL,6,FHe went on to say: "This is as clear a
OL,7,Fcase of murder as you are likely to
OL,8,Ffind.
OL,10,F"This defendant was having an argument
OL,11,Fwith her husband, Ian. She picked up a
OL,12,Flarge, sharp knife, and in a fit of
OL,13,Ftemper stabbed it into his back
OL,14,Fwithout any warning as he was walking
OL,15,Faway.
OL,17,F"She left the knife sticking out of
OL,18,Fhis back and walked off, her husband
OL,19,Ffollowing her and imploring her to
OL,20,Fpull the knife out."
