OL,11,Fthat she was the victim of a "coercive
OL,12,For controlling relationship". However,
OL,13,FMr Brunton said the prosecution
OL,14,Frefutes this.
OL,16,F"To stab a knife into someone's back
OL,17,Fwithout any warning is not an act of
OL,18,Fself-defence.
