OL,6,F"She may be a complex, troubled and
OL,7,Fsomewhat devious woman, but she
OL,8,Fdoesn't have a psychological condition
OL,9,Fthat would preclude her from being
OL,10,Fcriminally responsible for murder," he
OL,11,Fsaid.
OL,13,FMr Brunton added that the jury will
OL,14,Fhear more evidence that the pair had a
