OL,3,C'Devious' woman stabbed husband in the
OL,4,Cback after row, court told
OL,6,F"What 30-year marriage is without its
OL,7,Fcomplexities? Many marriages are far
OL,8,Ffrom happy. He did not torture,
OL,9,Fenslave or bully her. This defendant
OL,10,Fwas far from being a defenceless or
OL,11,Ftimid woman.
OL,13,F"They seemed to almost thrive on
OL,14,Fbickering and winding each other up.
OL,15,FIf anyone was the bully, we say it is
OL,16,Fthis woman here."
OL,18,FThe trial continues.
